%body.resist__body
  = render 'userheader'
  %main.registration__main
    %section.registration__main__container
      %h2.registration__main__head 会員情報入力
      %form.registration__main__form{action: "", method: "POST"}
        %input{name: "", type: "hidden", value: ""}/
        .user__form__content
          .user__form__group
            %label{for: "user__title"} ニックネーム
            %span.user__form__require 必須
            %input.user__form__input{name: "", placeholder: "例) ツルタさん", type: "text", value: ""}/
          .user__form__group
            %label{for: "user__title"} メールアドレス
            %span.user__form__require 必須
            %input.user__form__input{name: "", placeholder: "PC・携帯どちらでも可", type: "email", value: ""}/
          .user__form__group
            %label{for: "user__title"} パスワード
            %span.user__form__require 必須
            %input.user__form__input{name: "", placeholder: "6文字以上", type: "password"}/
          .user__form__group
            %label{for: "user__title"} パスワード (確認)
            %span.user__form__require 必須
            %input.user__form__input{name: "", placeholder: "6文字以上", type: "password"}/
          .user__form__group
            %h3.user__title__text 本人確認
            %p.user__title__text__inline
              安心・安全にご利用いただくために、お客さまの本人情報の登録にご協力ください。他のお客さまに公開されることはありません。
          .user__form__group
            %label{for: "user__title"} 姓 (全角)
            %span.user__form__require 必須
            %input.user__form__input{name: "", placeholder: "例) 雨笠", type: "text", value: ""}/
          .user__form__group
            %label{for: "user__title"} 名 (全角)
            %span.user__form__require 必須
            %input.user__form__input{name: "", placeholder: "例) 将", type: "text", value: ""}/
          .user__form__group
            %label{for: "user__title"} 姓カナ (全角)
            %span.user__form__require 必須
            %input.user__form__input{name: "", placeholder: "例) アマガサ", type: "text", value: ""}/
          .user__form__group
            %label{for: "user__title"} 名カナ (全角)
            %span.user__form__require 必須
            %input.user__form__input{name: "", placeholder: "例) ショウ", type: "text", value: ""}/
          .user__form__group
            %label{for: "user__title"} 生年月日
            %span.user__form__require 必須
            %br/
            .user__form__birthday
              .user__form__birthday__select
                %select.user__select__default.d__fa__select{name: "year"}
                  %option{value: ""} --
                  %option{value: "2019"} 2019
                  %option{value: "2018"} 2018
                  %option{value: "2017"} 2017
                  %option{value: "2016"} 2016
                  %option{value: "2015"} 2015
                  %option{value: "2014"} 2014
                  %option{value: "2013"} 2013
                  %option{value: "2012"} 2012
                  %option{value: "2011"} 2011
                  %option{value: "2010"} 2010
                  %option{value: "2009"} 2009
                  %option{value: "2008"} 2008
                  %option{value: "2007"} 2007
                  %option{value: "2006"} 2006
                  %option{value: "2005"} 2005
                  %option{value: "2004"} 2004
                  %option{value: "2003"} 2003
                  %option{value: "2002"} 2002
                  %option{value: "2001"} 2001
                  %option{value: "2000"} 2000
                 
                %i.user__select__default__arrow
              %span 年
              .user__form__birthday__select
                %select.user__select__default{:name => "month"}
                  %option{:value => ""} --
                  %option{:value => "1"} 1
                  %option{:value => "2"} 2
                  %option{:value => "3"} 3
                  %option{:value => "4"} 4
                  %option{:value => "5"} 5
                  %option{:value => "6"} 6
                  %option{:value => "7"} 7
                  %option{:value => "8"} 8
                  %option{:value => "9"} 9
                  %option{:value => "10"} 10
                  %option{:value => "11"} 11
                  %option{:value => "12"} 12
                %i.user__select__default__arrow
              %span 月
              .user__form__birthday__select
                %select.user__select__default{name: "day"}
                  %option{value: ""} --
                %i.icon-arrow-bottom
              %span 日
            %input{name: "", type: "hidden", value: ""}/
            .clearfix
          %p.user__form__infomation
            ※ 本人情報は正しく入力してください。会員登録後、修正するにはお時間を頂く場合があります。
        .user__form__content
          %input{name: "after_save_callback", type: "hidden", value: ""}/
          .user__form__group
            .user__form__recaptcha{"data-sitekey" => ""}
              %div{style: "width: 304px; height: 78px;"}
                %div
                  %iframe{frameborder: "0", height: "78", name: "", role: "presentation", sandbox: "", scrolling: "no", src: "", width: "304"}
                %textarea#user__form__recaptcha__id.g-recaptcha-response{name: "user__form__recaptcha", style: "width: 250px; height: 40px; border: 1px solid rgb(193, 193, 193); margin: 10px 25px; padding: 0px; resize: none; display: none;"}
          .user__form__group
            %p.user__form__infomation
              「次へ進む」のボタンを押すことにより、
              %a.user__text__decoration{href: "#", target: "_blank"}> 利用規約
              に同意したものとみなします
          %button.user__form__botton{type: "submit"} 次へ進む
          .user__form__group
            %p.user__form__other
              %a.user__form__other__info{href: "", target: "_blank"}
                本人情報の登録について#{fa_icon("angle-right lg")}
  = render 'subfooter'

